room_title: Escape room "The Mayfield Manor" by Unlocked Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_description: In the Roaring 20’s, during an age of gangsters and prohibition, going out for dinner and drinks isn’t that easy. While you and some friends are at a dinner party at the Mayfield Manor, you hear gunshots and stumble into the study to hide out only to find yourself locked inside. You have 55 minutes to figure out the secrets before the cops, or worse the mobsters, show up and you do not want to be there when that happens.
